{"type":"answer","id":2948,"parentType":"question","parentId":677,"uid":54,"contents":"有的。<br>\n<br>\n镇外八年级江学社和Rayista org-MogicGroup江联合在2018.8.17组织活动，欢迎镇江，扬州附近的蛤丝来参加。<br>\n<br>\n目前有两套方案：<br>\n<br>\n1.买华莱士外卖，坐公交车到镇江市句容市「宝华山国家森林公园」聚会，据说在这个山上跑步会跑得特别快。<br>\n<br>\n2.骑车，从镇江到扬州，买华莱士吃，通过「镇扬汽渡」，这个汽渡有他的题字。<br>\n<br>\n镇江和扬州附近的蛤丝如果有更好的方案欢迎交流。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180507/5f04c445a05c48bd34efb922439124f5.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180507/5f04c445a05c48bd34efb922439124f5.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180507/5f04c445a05c48bd34efb922439124f5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180507/c15f98f9dc3629e64685ed7fbaed552b.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180507/c15f98f9dc3629e64685ed7fbaed552b.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180507/c15f98f9dc3629e64685ed7fbaed552b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;","date":"2018-05-07","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}